<lb ed="I" n="0153a00" type="honorific"/><cb:mulu level="2" type="其他">額</cb:mulu><head>額</head>
<lb ed="I" n="0153a01" type="honorific"/><p xml:id="pI01p0153a0101">大齊
<lb ed="I" n="0153a02" type="honorific"/>趙郡
<lb ed="I" n="0153a03" type="honorific"/>王□
<lb ed="I" n="0153a04" type="honorific"/>□□
<lb ed="I" n="0153a05" type="honorific"/>之碑</p>
</cb:div>
<cb:div>
<lb ed="I" n="0153b00" type="honorific"/><cb:mulu level="2" type="其他">本文</cb:mulu><head>本文</head>
<lb ed="I" n="0153b01" type="honorific"/><p xml:id="pI01p0153b0101"><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">蓋</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">聞</unclear>珠林琁室。現崑崙之中。銀闕金宮。跱蓬萊之上。居之□<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">幽</unclear>。登之乃靈。逐雨隨風。懸殊六通之<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">果</unclear>。黃衣丹椹。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">亦</unclear>非四<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">類</unclear>之味。況□陽止□之洞。<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">省</unclear>□□大帝之□。□□
<lb ed="I" n="0153b02" type="honorific"/>生半天之山。七盧入香煙之岳。伏膺道術。始學牛毛。於我法門。事均驢乳。次復月光童子。戲天台之傍。仁祠浮圖。繞嵩高之側。行藏比於幻化。出沒放於淨土。弗□□□。
<lb ed="I" n="0153b03" type="honorific"/>罕逢濡足。及於金臺羅漢。遠住東海。瓊樹聲聞。遙家西域。承風問道。此實闕如。豈若太玄<note n="0153001" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30479"/>＝所【史】</note><app n="0153001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">所</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30479"/></rdg></app>都。化作<note n="0153002" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𦀇＝經【史】</note><app n="0153002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">經</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𦀇</rdg></app>行之境。真人<app type="star" corresp="#0153001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">所</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30479"/></rdg></app>府。翻成息心之地。黃河之北。忽出育王之龕。<note n="0153003" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">䓗＝蔥【史】</note><app n="0153003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">蔥</lem><rdg wit="【原】">䓗</rdg></app>□
<lb ed="I" n="0153b04" type="honorific"/>之<note n="0153004" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">柬＝東【史】</note><app n="0153004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">東</lem><rdg wit="【原】">柬</rdg></app>。別有迦維之國。然燈避風之<note n="0153005" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𠁅＝處【史】</note><app n="0153005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">處</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𠁅</rdg></app>。服藥息務之<app type="star" corresp="#0153001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">所</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30479"/></rdg></app>。和合戾止。有朱山焉。其地則上應琁星。下分<note n="0153006" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30928"/>＝全【史】</note><app n="0153006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">全</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30928"/></rdg></app>趙。邑迹靈丘。念黑貂之為珥。峰連牛飲。吐白陸之滋川。重嶺<note n="0153007" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30885"/>＝概【史】</note><app n="0153007"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">概</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30885"/></rdg></app>雲。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">苙</unclear>
<lb ed="I" n="0153b05" type="honorific"/>人或凡。曲<note n="0153008" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𡼏＝澗【史】</note><app n="0153008"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">澗</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𡼏</rdg></app>無<note n="0153009" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30886"/>＝底【史】</note><app n="0153009"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">底</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30886"/></rdg></app>。瞻天謂<note n="0153010" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">窓＝窗【史】</note><app n="0153010"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">窗</lem><rdg wit="【原】">窓</rdg></app>。晨光東壑。類湯谷密<note n="0153011" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𨒛＝邇【史】</note><app n="0153011"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">邇</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𨒛</rdg></app>。暮色西巘。<note n="0153012" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30888"/>＝怪【史】</note><app n="0153012"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">怪</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30888"/></rdg></app>崦嵫咫尺。<note n="0153013" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">隂＝陰【史】</note><app n="0153013"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">陰</lem><rdg wit="【原】">隂</rdg></app>冰夏素。想逼燭龍。陽木冬青。意近火<note n="0153014" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𣆨＝鼠【史】</note><app n="0153014"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">鼠</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𣆨</rdg></app>。重巖之面有<note n="0153015" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30890"/>＝瀑【史】</note><app n="0153015"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">瀑</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30890"/></rdg></app>布焉。至於春泉初涌。秋水時至。蕭
<lb ed="I" n="0153b06" type="honorific"/><note n="0153016" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">樤＝條【史】</note><app n="0153016"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">條</lem><rdg wit="【原】">樤</rdg></app>圓注。擬虹氛而上昇。散亂高流。狀天河之懸瀉。若乃金花瓊實。暎日香風。玉酒石膏。除飢卻老。羊腸九坂。<note n="0153017" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">虵＝蛇【史】</note><app n="0153017"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">蛇</lem><rdg wit="【原】">虵</rdg></app>盤九曲。驅龍從<note n="0153018" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𧆞＝虎【史】</note><app n="0153018"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">虎</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𧆞</rdg></app>。一見而不歸。控鵠<note n="0153019" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">乗＝乘【史】</note><app n="0153019"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">乘</lem><rdg wit="【原】">乗</rdg></app>鸞。蹔遊而忘返。定
<lb ed="I" n="0153b07" type="honorific"/>州定國寺。禪師僧標身重<note n="0153020" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𢦶＝戒【史】</note><app n="0153020"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">戒</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𢦶</rdg></app>珠。心倫堅石。時和人俗。不染世塵。以其山<app type="star" corresp="#0153005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">處</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𠁅</rdg></app>閑虛。林幽爽曠。香珍叶住地之德。清靜賞仁人之心。乃施淨財。云為禪室。於茲廿有餘年矣。背
<lb ed="I" n="0153b08" type="honorific"/>兔頭之嶺。構柏堂之谷。別房覓崎<note n="0153021" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">岴＝嶇【史】</note><app n="0153021"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">嶇</lem><rdg wit="【原】">岴</rdg></app>之岫。離館逐<note n="0153022" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30891"/>＝低【史】</note><app n="0153022"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">低</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30891"/></rdg></app>昂之嶮。交藤代幄。懸葛當帷。<note n="0153023" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30892"/>＝鑿【史】</note><app n="0153023"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">鑿</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30892"/></rdg></app>石開塗。披榛置<note n="0153024" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30893"/>＝徑【史】</note><app n="0153024"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">徑</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30893"/></rdg></app>。因山結宇。無勞一匱之勤。即水縈池。非求百姓之力。霧集懃定之
<lb ed="I" n="0153b09" type="honorific"/>侶。雲歸無漏之人。<note n="0153025" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30401"/>＝正【史】</note><app n="0153025"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">正</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30401"/></rdg></app>念不虧。息心相<note n="0153026" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">継＝繼【史】</note><app n="0153026"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">繼</lem><rdg wit="【原】">継</rdg></app>。頭堪孕鳥。心成竹<app type="star" corresp="#0153017"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">蛇</lem><rdg wit="【原】">虵</rdg></app>。採椽茅屋。<note n="0153027" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30894"/>＝藜【史】</note><app n="0153027"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">藜</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30894"/></rdg></app>羹粟飯。七益不受。三淨不食。是真<note n="0153028" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30895"/>＝苦【史】</note><app n="0153028"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">苦</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30895"/></rdg></app>行。是實頭陀。鐘韻應霜。梵聲傳谷。<app type="star" corresp="#0153018"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">虎</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𧆞</rdg></app>音纔振。風神散<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">非</unclear>時
<lb ed="I" n="0153b10" type="honorific"/>之花。魚鱗已舉。雨伯造清涼之氣。百鳥競鳴。學黑蜂之唱無我。萬籟爭響。寫天樂之娛法王。聞和雅音。咸無生忍。屬　　大齊之馭九有。累聖重<note n="0153029" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30896"/>＝規【史】</note><app n="0153029"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">規</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30896"/></rdg></app>。羲軒之流。炎昊之<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">輩</unclear>。
<lb ed="I" n="0153b11" type="honorific"/>出東震。握北<note n="0153030" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30897"/>＝斗【史】</note><app n="0153030"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">斗</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30897"/></rdg></app>。擊玉<note n="0153031" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30898"/>＝鼓【史】</note><app n="0153031"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">鼓</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30898"/></rdg></app>。轉金輪。前疑後承。左賢右<note n="0153032" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30899"/>＝戚【史】</note><app n="0153032"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">戚</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30899"/></rdg></app>。數當於天運。名上於河<note n="0153033" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">啚＝圖【史】</note><app n="0153033"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">圖</lem><rdg wit="【原】">啚</rdg></app>。入作股<note n="0153034" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𦙶＝肱【史】</note><app n="0153034"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">肱</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𦙶</rdg></app>。出為蕃屏。使持節都<note n="0153035" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𥆳＝督【史】</note><app n="0153035"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">督</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𥆳</rdg></app>定幽安平東燕滄瀛諸軍事撫軍將軍儀同三司定州
<lb ed="I" n="0153b12" type="honorific"/><note n="0153036" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30914"/>＝刺【史】</note><app n="0153036"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">刺</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30914"/></rdg></app>史六州大都<app type="star" corresp="#0153035"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">督</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𥆳</rdg></app>趙郡<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">王</unclear>高叡。枝流姜水。氣別大風。昔殷周以稷契立功。虞漢藉軒唐之德。<note n="0153037" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𣸪＝復【史】</note><app n="0153037"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">復</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𣸪</rdg></app>有<note n="0153038" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">揔＝摠【史】</note><app n="0153038"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">摠</lem><rdg wit="【原】">揔</rdg></app>農皇之緒。兼尚父之勳。光奄宇宙。義高前篆。祖同王季。彰積德之<note n="0153039" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">苻＝符【史】</note><app n="0153039"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">符</lem><rdg wit="【原】">苻</rdg></app>。
<lb ed="I" n="0153b13" type="honorific"/><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">考</unclear>即劉文。協內謀之議。<note n="0153040" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30926"/>＝休【史】</note><app n="0153040"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">休</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30926"/></rdg></app>徵遠降。爰誕異人。封自東門。土分北社。多能將聖。上稟天知。<note n="0153041" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30900"/>＝幼【史】</note><app n="0153041"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">幼</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30900"/></rdg></app><note n="0153042" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30901"/>＝秉【史】</note><app n="0153042"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">秉</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30901"/></rdg></app><app type="star" corresp="#0153017"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">蛇</lem><rdg wit="【原】">虵</rdg></app>珠。雀臺擒□。□成麟角。<app type="star" corresp="#0153018"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">虎</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𧆞</rdg></app>殿論儒。辯樂三雍。富河澗之典。<note n="0153043" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30902"/>＝驂【史】</note><app n="0153043"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">驂</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30902"/></rdg></app>駕四馬。高柏
<lb ed="I" n="0153b14" type="honorific"/><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">樑</unclear>之勾。吐握思賢。安勞郭隗之<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">策</unclear>。水鏡知士。何有鄒陽之書。故令司馬願遊<g ref="#CB30883"/>解。武騎<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">邯</unclear>鄲對見。雅伏天人。忠以奉公。惠以施□。□神敬鬼。織天成地。心將冥會。非<app type="star" corresp="#0153037"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">復</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𣸪</rdg></app>爻
<lb ed="I" n="0153b15" type="honorific"/><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">象</unclear>攸知。迹出人表。亦豈名言<app type="star" corresp="#0153001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">所</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30479"/></rdg></app>測。劉蒼德茂。彌事謙下。馬孚尊寵。不以為榮。至夫恒嶺崇高。虞巡北岳。中山<note n="0153044" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30903"/>＝舊【史】</note><app n="0153044"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">舊</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30903"/></rdg></app>國。漢<note n="0153045" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30904"/>＝號【史】</note><app n="0153045"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">號</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30904"/></rdg></app>東蕃。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">帝</unclear>摯唐侯。昔封此邑。魏文太子。<app type="star" corresp="#0153037"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">復</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𣸪</rdg></app>鎮斯城。五
<lb ed="I" n="0153b16" type="honorific"/><note n="0153046" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30905"/>＝陘【史】</note><app n="0153046"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">陘</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30905"/></rdg></app>傍通。四關斜<note n="0153047" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𢫾＝指【史】</note><app n="0153047"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">指</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𢫾</rdg></app>。荊卿易水。含燕寒而北流。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">王</unclear>霸呼<note n="0153048" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">沲＝沱【史】</note><app n="0153048"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">沱</lem><rdg wit="【原】">沲</rdg></app>。浮漢冰而南<note n="0153049" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">脉＝脈【史】</note><app n="0153049"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">脈</lem><rdg wit="【原】">脉</rdg></app>。地中天府。聞蘇子之言。境<note n="0153050" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𥦽＝寔【史】</note><app n="0153050"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">寔</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𥦽</rdg></app>神州。具盧□<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">之</unclear>說。海城七十。僅譬閭井。雲夢八九。寧方藪澤。連<note n="0153051" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB18746"/>＝甍【史】</note><app n="0153051"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">甍</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB18746"/></rdg></app>接
<lb ed="I" n="0153b17" type="honorific"/>棟。煦氣成虹。袨服靚莊。揮汗如雨。先公佐<note n="0153052" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30762"/>＝世【史】</note><app n="0153052"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">世</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30762"/></rdg></app>。<note n="0153053" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">甞＝嘗【史】</note><app n="0153053"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">嘗</lem><rdg wit="【原】">甞</rdg></app>歷斯蕃。　皇弟分陝。每為是牧。帝室維<note n="0153054" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𨎰＝翰【史】</note><app n="0153054"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">翰</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𨎰</rdg></app>。莫此之尤。劇齊<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">中</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">之</unclear>□□。□<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">河</unclear>內之擇士。遂乃褰<note n="0153055" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30907"/>＝襜【史】</note><app n="0153055"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">襜</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30907"/></rdg></app>明視。戴冕來遊。繡轂朱輪。
<lb ed="I" n="0153b18" type="honorific"/><note n="0153056" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30908"/>＝聯【史】</note><app n="0153056"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">聯</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30908"/></rdg></app>清塵於往迹。鳴金繁唱。接高風之遺響。前後韋氏。大小馮君。挍德談榮。飛天伏地。屈其大道。<note n="0153057" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30909"/>＝烹【史】</note><app n="0153057"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">烹</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30909"/></rdg></app>乎小鮮。張瑟調琴。裁縠製錦。賤分<app type="star" corresp="#0153013"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">陰</lem><rdg wit="【原】">隂</rdg></app>於尺璧。子<note n="0153058" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30910"/>＝黎【史】</note><app n="0153058"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">黎</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30910"/></rdg></app>庶而<note n="0153059" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">蒱＝蒲【史】</note><app n="0153059"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">蒲</lem><rdg wit="【原】">蒱</rdg></app>蘆。始布六條。
<lb ed="I" n="0153b19" type="honorific"/>尋能一䛀。移風化俗。詎待七年。去<note n="0153060" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30911"/>＝煞【史】</note><app n="0153060"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">煞</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30911"/></rdg></app><note n="0153061" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB31163"/>＝勝【史】</note><app n="0153061"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">勝</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB31163"/></rdg></app>殘。何求百歲。政明民訟。蚩郭賀之荊州。甄屈搜賢。鄙山濤之<note n="0153062" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB31164"/>＝冀【史】</note><app n="0153062"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">冀</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB31164"/></rdg></app>部。百城順軌。四時感德。<app type="star" corresp="#0153013"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">陰</lem><rdg wit="【原】">隂</rdg></app>陽隨意。綱目如旨。寧復二縣不雨。方待
<lb ed="I" n="0153b20" type="honorific"/>車行。三郡無堪。更令徵黜。德既行焉。功亦成焉。田有遺<note n="0153063" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">粮＝糧【史】</note><app n="0153063"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">糧</lem><rdg wit="【原】">粮</rdg></app>。菓無外援。蹍虺<app type="star" corresp="#0153017"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">蛇</lem><rdg wit="【原】">虵</rdg></app>而尾<app type="star" corresp="#0153018"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">虎</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𧆞</rdg></app>豹。<note n="0153064" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30912"/>＝窺【史】</note><app n="0153064"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">窺</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30912"/></rdg></app>烏鵲<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">而</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">養</unclear>鳳<note n="0153065" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">䳨＝凰【史】</note><app n="0153065"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">凰</lem><rdg wit="【原】">䳨</rdg></app>。□車迄今。初歷七祀。自人皇出谷。分長九州。<app type="star" corresp="#0153042"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">秉</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30901"/></rdg></app>旄作牧。蓋無常
<lb ed="I" n="0153b21" type="honorific"/>限。然梁習臨并。止餘十載。<note n="0153066" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">祌＝神【史】</note><app n="0153066"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">神</lem><rdg wit="【原】">祌</rdg></app>暠<app type="star" corresp="#0153005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">處</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𠁅</rdg></app>益。唯乞一年。恐須<app type="star" corresp="#0153025"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">正</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30401"/></rdg></app>階台。載馳綸<note n="0153067" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30913"/>＝綍【史】</note><app n="0153067"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">綍</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30913"/></rdg></app>。借君請帝。向天門而難<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">止</unclear>。<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">臥</unclear>道興□。望雲車而無極。四民<app type="star" corresp="#0153001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">所</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30479"/></rdg></app>以相告。萬里<app type="star" corresp="#0153001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">所</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30479"/></rdg></app>以先憂。尋夫羊公。<app type="star" corresp="#0153036"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">刺</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30914"/></rdg></app>
<lb ed="I" n="0153b22" type="honorific"/>□□□。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">連</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">率</unclear>梁楚。宗令周邵。親賢並播。<note n="0153068" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30477"/>＝椒【史】</note><app n="0153068"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">椒</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30477"/></rdg></app>蘭俱懸。日月未<app type="star" corresp="#0153053"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">嘗</lem><rdg wit="【原】">甞</rdg></app>矜。萬物觀一己。脆同蘆葦。空似<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">芭</unclear>蕉。縱四毒<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">之</unclear>□。任五情之馬。與夫解<app type="star" corresp="#0153001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">所</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30479"/></rdg></app>未解。度<app type="star" corresp="#0153001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">所</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30479"/></rdg></app>未度。安可以相論哉。我
<lb ed="I" n="0153b23" type="honorific"/>王<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">夙</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">殖</unclear>善<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">根</unclear>。□<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">剎</unclear>利種。以為靈光之殿。遠謝微妙之臺。<note n="0153069" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30915"/>＝黼【史】</note><app n="0153069"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">黼</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30915"/></rdg></app>黻之衣。誠乖精進之鎧。故以先覺而寤後覺。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">後</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">燈</unclear>而助先燈。將欲遠持三界。盡置十<note n="0153070" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𧨅＝善【史】</note><app n="0153070"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">善</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𧨅</rdg></app>。何直<app type="star" corresp="#0153002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">經</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𦀇</rdg></app>緯文武。粉澤禮
<lb ed="I" n="0153b24" type="honorific"/>樂。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">唯</unclear>然而已乎。□聞道場。攝心<note n="0153071" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">廻＝迴【史】</note><app n="0153071"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">迴</lem><rdg wit="【原】">廻</rdg></app>向。隨憘供設為福田。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">王</unclear>因以其寺名粵□□。宣尼論至道之時。乃有斯稱。軒轅念天師之教。且<app type="star" corresp="#0153039"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">符</lem><rdg wit="【原】">苻</rdg></app>今旨。淨心<app type="star" corresp="#0153001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">所</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30479"/></rdg></app>宅。豈與同年。兼於此伽
<lb ed="I" n="0153b25" type="honorific"/>藍。更興靈塔。光光流曜。比秋月之華。蓬蓬茂出。如白雲之舉。銅槃上竦。遠承仙露。金鐸相鳴。遙驚山鬼。又<app type="star" corresp="#0153037"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">復</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𣸪</rdg></app>運藍田之玉。採荊山之珍。鏤殫變化。圖窮相好。繢渥不汙。用
<lb ed="I" n="0153b26" type="honorific"/>□無染之<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">身</unclear>。夜光遍體。因現神通之色。於是竹間精舍。樹下講堂。光飾侔青鳥之蓮。珍華<note n="0153072" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30916"/>＝奪【史】</note><app n="0153072"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">奪</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30916"/></rdg></app>白牛之駕。仙靈拖棟。或真聖之<app type="star" corresp="#0153019"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">乘</lem><rdg wit="【原】">乗</rdg></app>煙。雲氣<note n="0153073" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𡸁＝垂【史】</note><app n="0153073"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">垂</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𡸁</rdg></app><app type="star" corresp="#0153051"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">甍</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB18746"/></rdg></app>。<note n="0153074" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">乱＝亂【史】</note><app n="0153074"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">亂</lem><rdg wit="【原】">乱</rdg></app>峰巖之觸石。是知無生無
<lb ed="I" n="0153b27" type="honorific"/>□。□有鵠林。不即不離。茲亦鷲嶺。道本一准。勿輕像法之期。佛乃<app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">无</lem><rdg wit="【原】【史】">旡</rdg></app><note n="0153075" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30565"/>＝邊【史】</note><app n="0153075"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">邊</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30565"/></rdg></app>。何偏王舍之界。寺去州城餘二百里。扶<note n="0153076" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">桒＝桑【史】</note><app n="0153076"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">桑</lem><rdg wit="【原】">桒</rdg></app>初曉。楊枝始嚼。塵消氣滅。霧卷霞除。昇高峰。<note n="0153077" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30917"/>＝望【史】</note><app n="0153077"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">望</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30917"/></rdg></app>都邑。朱
<lb ed="I" n="0153b28" type="honorific"/><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">樓</unclear>紫閣。真雲中之化欲來。綠樹丹城。像域外之飛將至。分明可見。異隴首之望平川。踈散高情。踰岱宗之小天下。壯哉峻極。麗矣莊嚴。何但名相佛土。頗<app type="star" corresp="#0153058"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">黎</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30910"/></rdg></app>為地。法<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">明</unclear>出
<lb ed="I" n="0153b29" type="honorific"/>世。天宮近人。齊聖廣淵也如彼。菩提道<note n="0153078" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30918"/>＝身【史】</note><app n="0153078"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">身</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30918"/></rdg></app>也如此。自可生蓮花於<note n="0153079" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30919"/>＝鬲【史】</note><app n="0153079"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">鬲</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30919"/></rdg></app>子。樊烈火於魔宮。屏息而獲法雲。翹足而俟授記。寧<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">止</unclear>延　皇家卜年之數。增我　后　王佐之功。
<lb ed="I" n="0153b30" type="honorific"/>井藤相促。城芥將滿。庶願力護持。群神肅翼。須<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">彌</unclear>腐敗。<app type="star" corresp="#0153061"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">勝</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB31163"/></rdg></app>地莫渝。玄圃飛浮。神山恒固。今歲在<note n="0153080" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30404"/>＝赤【史】</note><app n="0153080"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">赤</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30404"/></rdg></app><note n="0153081" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30921"/>＝奮【史】</note><app n="0153081"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">奮</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30921"/></rdg></app>。時惟青秖。陽殖官杏。日望月桂。<note n="0153082" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30922"/>＝斲【史】</note><app n="0153082"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">斲</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30922"/></rdg></app>磨瑊玏。明揚<note n="0153083" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">皷＝鼓【史】</note><app n="0153083"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">鼓</lem><rdg wit="【原】">皷</rdg></app>鍾。縱漢帝種桃。屢
<lb ed="I" n="0153b31" type="honorific"/>獲花菓。麻姑看海。數移陵陸。猶望有類粟山。記戊申之歲。更同荊峴。見望拜之碑。無愧之詞。乃為銘曰。
<lb ed="I" n="0153b32" type="honorific"/>即林嘉遁。歸山長<note n="0153084" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30927"/>＝住【史】</note><app n="0153084"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">住</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30927"/></rdg></app>。未極人天。猶居塵壤。我有福地。<app type="star" corresp="#0153006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">全</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30928"/></rdg></app>疑安養。閣暎珠羅。樓懸金<note n="0153085" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">䋄＝網【史】</note><app n="0153085"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">網</lem><rdg wit="【原】">䋄</rdg></app>。峰高萬刃。<app type="star" corresp="#0153008"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">澗</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𡼏</rdg></app>遠千尋。煙雲出入。仙聖登臨。谷幽虛囀。松高自吟。紫芝咸迾。丹桂成□。
<lb ed="I" n="0153b33" type="honorific"/>彼有人焉。創茲虛境。高<app type="star" corresp="#0153010"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">窗</lem><rdg wit="【原】">窓</rdg></app>蔭柏。危櫚承嶺。野曠村稀。巖空人靜。草呼風氣。池搖月影。嘿形端拱。凝神丘壑。搖錫褰衣。遨遊林薄。思滅毒火。求分良藥。遠棄形骸。蕭然寥□。
<lb ed="I" n="0153b34" type="honorific"/>曆窮於坎。倉精受命。陵躪百王。懸衡七政。洛<app type="star" corresp="#0153039"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">符</lem><rdg wit="【原】">苻</rdg></app><note n="0153086" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">効＝效【史】</note><app n="0153086"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">效</lem><rdg wit="【原】">効</rdg></app>祉。河文標聖。朝眾水神。國多天鏡。本枝磐石。如珪如璧。龍變成章。鵬飛舉翮。閤延髦士。庭多捐客。高義盈門。清談滿席。
<lb ed="I" n="0153b35" type="honorific"/>燕南趙北。奇士爰臻。盧河通氣。白壤飄塵。<app type="star" corresp="#0153013"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">陰</lem><rdg wit="【原】">隂</rdg></app>陽<app type="star" corresp="#0153001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">所</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30479"/></rdg></app>合。風雨攸均。輕軒高蓋。來慰斯民。卬泥作豉。牧羊調馬。德通靈物。謠成風雅。寬猛春秋。愛畏冬夏。并州陵段。<app type="star" corresp="#0153062"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">冀</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB31164"/></rdg></app>方踰□。
<lb ed="I" n="0153b36" type="honorific"/>爰觀六趣。尚想三塗。香珍<note n="0153087" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30923"/>＝薝【史】</note><app n="0153087"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">薝</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30923"/></rdg></app>匐。道慕拘盧。化城度嶮。抨酪求蘇。既雕宮觀。有類蓬<note n="0153088" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB31177"/>＝壺【史】</note><app n="0153088"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">壺</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB31177"/></rdg></app>。百雉攸遠。九成<note n="0153089" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30924"/>＝迢【史】</note><app n="0153089"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">迢</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30924"/></rdg></app><note n="0153090" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𨘬＝遰【史】</note><app n="0153090"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">遰</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𨘬</rdg></app>。薄霧輕籠。微煙少<note n="0153091" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𦿔＝蔽【史】</note><app n="0153091"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">蔽</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𦿔</rdg></app>。光風新靜。暾暉初麗。極目相望。地<app type="star" corresp="#0153019"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">乘</lem><rdg wit="【原】">乗</rdg></app>天際。
<lb ed="I" n="0153b37" type="honorific"/><app type="star" corresp="#0153030"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">斗</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30897"/></rdg></app><app type="star" corresp="#0153071"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">迴</lem><rdg wit="【原】">廻</rdg></app>南北。日轉西東。遑遑馳驟。抵速<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">人</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">中</unclear>。地煎熱水。天壞<note n="0153092" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">灾＝災【史】</note><app n="0153092"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">災</lem><rdg wit="【原】">灾</rdg></app>風。願將此<app type="star" corresp="#0153005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">處</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𠁅</rdg></app>。懸置虛空。
<lb ed="I" n="0153b38" type="honorific"/>　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　大齊天保八年歲在丁丑<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">二</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">月</unclear>戊辰十五日壬午刊記</p>
